 왔는데 미안하지만, 돌아가지 않을래?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"nnf02","expressionName":"sad01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"event173-04-038","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":8}],"windowDisplayName":"히마리","body":"응?\n일단 출연하는 사람을 취재하려고 하는데……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"event173-04-039","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"란","body":"아버지가 나가지 않게\n아직 설득 하고 있어.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"nnf03","expressionName":"sad01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"event173-04-040","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"치사토","body":"뭐? 출연하시는 분이…… 란 짱의 아버지야?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"event173-04-041","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"란","body":"아뇨, 반드시 막을게요!\n그런 건 제가 다 부끄러우니까요.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"nnf02","expressionName":"angry01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"event173-04-042","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":8}],"windowDisplayName":"히마리","body":"어째서~ 나오셔도 상관없잖아.\n란의 아버지가 나온다고 하면 모두 좋아할 거야!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"event173-04-043","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"란","body":"그러니까 싫다고!\n모카만 해도 분명 놀림거리로 삼을 테고","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"angry02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"event173-04-044","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":8}],"windowDisplayName":"히마리","body":"엥~ 잠깐만이라도 이야기했으면 좋겠는데~","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"event173-04-045","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"란","body":"히마리한테 협력하고 싶은 마음은 산더미 같지만……\n이것만큼은 절대로 안 돼. 미안","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName